---
const skills = [
  "JavaScript/TypeScript",
  "React/Vue.js",
  "Node.js",
  "Python",
  "AWS/Cloud",
  "Agile/Scrum"
];
---

<section id="about" class="py-24">
  <div class="max-w-prose mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="space-y-16 fade-in">
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium">About</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-body text-secondary dark:text-gray-400">
          <p>
            I'm a passionate Software Engineer with over 12 years of experience in building scalable applications
            and leading development teams. My journey in technology has been driven by a constant desire to learn
            and solve complex problems.
          </p>
          <p>
            Throughout my career, I've successfully delivered enterprise-level applications, mentored junior developers,
            and implemented efficient development processes that significantly improved team productivity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Technical Skills</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 stagger">
          {skills.map(skill => (
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-light dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-lg hover-lift">
              <span class="text-sm font-medium">{skill}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>